Request app/ebook to be added to Cellabus catalog
2015-05-29 00:05
For Teachers
To install an app or ebook on your students' iPads, it needs to be first approved and added to your school or district's Cellabus catalog.<br><br>To request the addition of an app or ebook, <b>click on the Request New App or Request New Ebook button on the Teacher Dashboard homepage</b>.<br><br><span style="line-height: 1.4em; background-color: rgb(249, 250, 251);">On the following page, enter the <b>iTunes id</b> of the app you want to add. <br><br>To get the iTunes id of an app, search for the app on a search engine like Google using the term <i>"App Name iTunes</i>". For instance: <i>ClassDojo iTunes</i>.&nbsp;<br></span><span style="line-height: 1.4em; background-color: rgb(249, 250, 251);"><br>The id you are looking for can be found in the URL of the app between id and ? http://itunes.apple.com/[country]/app/[App–Name]/id[</span><span style="font-weight: bolder; background-color: rgb(249, 250, 251);">iTunesID</span><span style="line-height: 1.4em; background-color: rgb(249, 250, 251);">]?mt=8<br></span><span style="line-height: 1.4em; background-color: rgb(249, 250, 251);"><br>For instance for ClassDojo, it's the</span><span style="line-height: 1.4em; background-color: rgb(249, 250, 251);">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-weight: bolder; background-color: rgb(249, 250, 251);">552602056</span><span style="line-height: 1.4em; background-color: rgb(249, 250, 251);">&nbsp;</span><img src="https://cellabus.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/article_attachments/201259099/Screen_Shot_2015-01-05_at_03.18.25.png" alt="" style="background-color: rgb(249, 250, 251);"><br><br>Once you have the iTunes ID, enter the same in the form and click the&nbsp;<b>﻿Find App&nbsp;</b>﻿or&nbsp;<b>﻿Find Ebook&nbsp;</b>﻿button.<br><br><span><img src="/static/articles/enter_id.png"><br></span><span style="line-height: 1.4em; background-color: rgb(249, 250, 251);"><br>If the correct iTunes ID is entered, the next page will show the appropriate app.&nbsp;<br></span><span><br>Now<b> enter the number of licenses you would like to request for your use </b>﻿and click the&nbsp;<b>﻿Submit Request&nbsp;</b>﻿button<b>.</b>&nbsp;<b>﻿<i>﻿This is required for both free and paid.&nbsp;</i></b></span><span style="color: rgb(41, 44, 51); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; line-height: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Cellabus will then send an email to your administrator with the request, who will then purchase the required licenses. Your admin will also associate the license and install the app to the devices in the class you selected in the request form.<br></span><span><br><span><img src="/static/articles/newapp.png"></span><br></span><br><span><br></span><br><br><br><div></div>
